          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Call this API to register a merchant and their domains. You can register domains in multiple requests. The API has a limit of 99 domain names per ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "partnerInternalMerchantIdentifier.",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Before making a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applepaywebmerchantregistrationapi/documentation/ApplePayWebMerchantRegistrationAPI/Register-Merchant",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " request, you must prepare each domain included in the request for verification. For more information on domain verification, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applepaywebmerchantregistrationapi/documentation/ApplePayWebMerchantRegistrationAPI/preparing-merchant-domains-for-verification",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This request returns no response body for a successful 200 response. Apple Pay servers register the relationship between the e-commerce partner, the merchant, and the merchant’s domains.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "To access the sandbox environment, use ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "POST",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "https://apple-pay-gateway-cert.apple.com/paymentservices/registerMerchant",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
